      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ELITE DELUXE (1) is a well performed dog and winner of 13 races who was in the minor money last time out at this track (22.42). Has a good record here at this journey. Although beaten ran one of the quickest times on the card last start. Good form should continue. HELLO CINDY LOU (2) unfancied latest but hit the ground running and gave a sight, holding on for a minor placing (27.81) at this track in a Free For All over 488m. Will give a great sight again. BRAVE ANNIE (6) goes very well this trip starting 32 times for 14 wins and seven minors. Comes off a (22.55) win last time, scoring by 1.5 lengths in a Free For All over 400m at this track. Suited here and expected to run well. GOLD SMIRCH (8) is always hard to beat when she races at this trip.",
